        <item>
            <title>【評測】Seraﬁm S3 雲端遊戲⼿掣　輕便舒適 + 支援多平台</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/serafilm-s3/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=serafilm-s3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/serafilm-s3/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:30:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Seraﬁm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Seraﬁm S3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222750</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>來自台灣的電競配件品牌 Serafim 近日推出了 Serafim S3 雲端遊戲手掣，除了支援 USB-C Android 手機外，更可跨平台連接雲端遊戲打造，使用 <span class="Y2IQFc" lang="zh-TW">Xbox Game Pass、GeForce Now、Steam Link 等平台在雲端暢遊熟悉的遊戲。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09297-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09297-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09297.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09312-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09312-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09312.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><h2>配件</h2><p>盒內有 Serafim S3 手機遊戲手掣本體、 USB-C to USB-C 充電線（分別為 1 米及 3.3 米）、一份説明書和一對握把，無論玩家手大手細也合用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09300-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09300-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09300.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲隨機附送的握把更加纖薄，適合手細的玩家</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09302-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09302-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09302.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左邊為原生握把，右邊則是隨附的纖薄握把</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09307-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09307-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09307.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲徒手就能輕鬆替換握把</p><h2>實測 &#8211; Google Play 遊戲</h2><p>這款遊戲手柄使用 USB-C 就能連接手提電話，惟暫未支援 iPhone 15，所以小編就使用 Android 電話連接 Serafim S3。不過要留意，試玩前需要先下載「Serafim Console」應用程式。小編試玩了超音鼠和 Asphalt 8。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-6-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-6-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-6-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲需要先下載此應用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09321-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09321-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09321.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-5-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-5-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-1-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-1-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09323-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09323-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09323.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223695" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-2-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-2-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223697" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-4-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-4-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由於 Serafim S3 使用 USB-C 連接，而非無線方式，因此按鍵基本上可以説是沒有延遲，而且其蘑菇掣非常順暢，沒有飄移問題。Serafim S3 操作鍵位和平常遊戲手掣一樣，小編試用後覺得手感不俗，唯一要彈的就是手柄構造較單薄，略嫌手感輕飄飄的。</p><h2>實測 &#8211; PlayStation 5</h2><p>小編另外嘗試使用電話連接 PS5 遊玩 PS5 上的遊戲。Serafim S3 官方表示不能使用 SONY 官方的應用程式，需要使用他們提供的「PSPlay:PS5 &amp; PS4 Remote Play」應用程式，而這個應用程式更索價港幣 50.9 元。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-2-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-2-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-2-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲需要先下載這個應用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-1-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-1-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-1-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲索價 50.9 元</p><p>其後就可連接 PS5 遊玩。小編就試玩了《聖獸之王》 和《FF 7 REBIRTH》。小編懷疑是 Wi-Fi 稍慢，明顯可見延遲頗為嚴重，玩 FF7 時延遲嚴重至影響正常遊玩體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09325-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09325-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09325.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《聖獸之王》</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09340-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09340-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09340.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲《FFVII Rebirth》</p><h2>總結</h2><p>如果平時喜歡使用手機裝置玩雲端遊戲的玩家，可以嘗試用 Serafim S3 手掣入門。小編試玩過這款手掣後，覺得手感頗舒適，而且手掣蘑菇掣沒有飄移問題，非常順暢。唯一要彈的是，小編是 PS5 玩家，而這款手掣的佈局是 XBOX 式 ABXY，需要些時間適應。除此之外，小編覺得這款手掣造工較為單薄，比較脆弱，而且如果要使用 PS5 Remote Play 的話，僅能夠使用非官方應用程式，該第三方應用程式除了索價 50.9 元外，更有資安隱患。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09335-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09335-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09335.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/serafilm-s3/review-2/">【評測】Seraﬁm S3 雲端遊戲⼿掣　輕便舒適 + 支援多平台</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
