            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225409</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日稍早前，我們報道過外媒爆料有關 PlayStation 5 Pro 的規格（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/">相關報道</a>），據報這批資料準確度甚高。以往官方一般不會對這類爆料作任何回應，但是次 SONY 罕有地就爆料文件展開內部調查，側面反映出這次的消息可信度極高，今年很有機會出現 PS5 Pro 新機。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">As expected, Sony has launched an internal investigation into the leaked documents on Trinity as it leaked during a third-party rollout. </p><p>Not sure on the implications yet as I don&#39;t think they can catch one individual, but Sony could reduce its third-party developer pool for new…</p><p>&mdash; Tom Henderson (@_Tom_Henderson_) <a href="https://twitter.com/_Tom_Henderson_/status/1769811233237065881?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 18, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>外媒《InsiderGaming》早前報道過 PS5 Pro 的規格，創辦人 Tom Henderson （X 帳户：<a href="https://twitter.com/_Tom_Henderson_">@_Tom_Henderson_</a>）昨日（19 日）在 X （前稱 Twitter）發文表示 Sony 已經就 PS5 Pro 規格洩漏展開內部調查，現階段尚未確認影響，而且據 Tom Henderson 估計 Sony 未有捉到洩密者，但估計 Sony 將會減少第三方開發者加入研發工作。</p><p>有興趣深入瞭解 Sony PlayStation 5 Pro 規格的朋友可以看看我們先前的報道。連結：<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/">https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/_Tom_Henderson_/status/1769811233237065881">Tom Henderson@X</a><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Pro 規格外洩　外媒：光線追蹤性能強 3 倍 + 支援 8K</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/17/ps5-pro-specs-2024/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Pro 傳年底推出　效能快 45% 支援更穩定輸出</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/14/ps5-16/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5「重大」系統更新　PS5 機身顯示燈更光 + 手掣聲量增大</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/sony-investiagte-ps5-pro/fun-tech/">PS5 Pro 規格洩漏文件或屬實，外媒：SONY 已展開內部調查</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
